review_content: Processor was nice and too good in this price point and for sure you can go with it.If you have motherboard like g41(lga 775)Packaging was also very good but I will recommend you to pls check the processor once in the front of the delivery guy about it conditions if it's not looking good pls donot take the product.Order it again The product i received was good and nice completely looking like new.I'm very happy with the purchase.

It's really a good product, working perfectly with my intel DG31PR motherboard and no need for formatting pc after installation, sellers provide me jenuine (2nd or 3rd hand whatever it is)good product.

+5 stars for providing thermal paste with the processor otherwise it would have cost Rs.200-300 more. The processor is working as intended. I benchmarked both my previous (C2D E4300) and this processor (overclocked to 3.3 Ghz) on Cinebench R23 and the results are in the images I've uploaded.
